summary: My main drive is to discover new scientific ideas and to share these ideas with others. I greatly enjoy to use the abstract tools science gives me to solve the complex problems provided by society. In addition, I gain a lot of energy from explaining and transferring these abstract results to a broad class of people, from my fellow researchers to the general public.
